    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简介</strong></h2><br>《躲或死》是一个以黑暗世界为背景的非对称多人恐怖游戏。玩家可以在快速的捉迷藏游戏中扮演幸存者和猎人的角色。幸存者必须整装待发，找到并重新启动被遗弃的采掘机，并在黑暗完全耗尽它们之前逃脱。如果幸存者不想面对某种死亡，则需要共同努力，设置陷阱并保持快速前进的步伐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/b96214c8fa2ed98a2fdfff7280655982.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/b96214c8fa2ed98a2fdfff7280655982.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/b96214c8fa2ed98a2fdfff7280655982.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><br><strong>紧张、快节奏的动作游戏</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/4339d3c2aa6aaebfc6cb0b71f9a13632.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/4339d3c2aa6aaebfc6cb0b71f9a13632.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/4339d3c2aa6aaebfc6cb0b71f9a13632.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>流动性是《躲或死》中的重点。幸存者需要通过滑动、超级冲刺和跳跃跨过障碍物，由此引发更加激烈的追逐及突破猎人视线的方式。地图是从头开始专门构建的，同时还考虑了垂直性、隐藏性和移动性。幸存者和猎人可以在游戏开始时探索3幅独特的地图，随着游戏的进行，其中会添加更多的地图。<br><br><strong>有意义的进展</strong><br>收集黑暗并非无意义；使用收集到的黑暗，玩家可以通过福利来升级他们的角色，从而为猎人和幸存者赋予全新的能力。超过100种改变玩法的福利，您会发现自己将各种负载组合在一起，可以极大地改变避免死亡和处理死亡的方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/354c12657fa5cefc6447d3b1462d71ad.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=158 /></span><br>我们的俱乐部季度通行证和基于等级的装扮箱-都是100％免费的。使用我们的俱乐部的100级别，解锁新猎手、装扮、各式各样的幸存者服装以及更多特权。或者，你可以升级角色，解锁包含供你的角色使用的各种独特装扮的装扮箱。<br><br><strong>专用服务器</strong><br>《躲或死》具有全球专用服务器，可通过Microsoft Azure实现流畅的游戏玩法以及AAA质量的网络性能和响应能力。<br><br><strong>无与伦比的定制</strong><br>拥有数百种可解锁的角色装扮，以及数十种塑造幸存者外观的方法，创建梦想中的角色如此简单。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/e7ebff2f77fa563c15c07cc4e1b8017c.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/e7ebff2f77fa563c15c07cc4e1b8017c.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/e7ebff2f77fa563c15c07cc4e1b8017c.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/c5a39f7cb10b967f4426532d05271922.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/c5a39f7cb10b967f4426532d05271922.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/c5a39f7cb10b967f4426532d05271922.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>众多猎人</strong><br>为了适应所有玩家的游戏风格，2020年将推出4位猎人，且有3位猎人投入制作，每个角色都将享有与众不同的体验。从远程猎人到超现实恐怖，肯定有适合你的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/8385bbc2e577bdd887894cc5736ee688.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/8385bbc2e577bdd887894cc5736ee688.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/8385bbc2e577bdd887894cc5736ee688.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/bc78866ddd79facacd947b42d183ae51.poster.avif?t=1607993098\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/bc78866ddd79facacd947b42d183ae51.webm?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/731620/extras/bc78866ddd79facacd947b42d183ae51.mp4?t=1607993098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>与朋友一起游戏</strong><br>《躲或死》完全支持Steam组大厅，和你的朋友们一起面对黑暗",
